{"type":null,"faqId":11667,"title":"G610-U00(G610+)   WLAN待机的时候会自动断开，怎么解决，手机默认是什么设置？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">这个问题是休眠策略的问题。进入的方法：在主屏幕，点击</span> <b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">无线和网络</span></b><span> &gt; <b>WLAN</b></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，再点击菜单键</span><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33075\" width=\"26\" height=\"21\" alt=\"\" /></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">并进入<b>高级</b></span><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在休眠状态下保持</span><span>WLAN</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">连接</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，设置为“始终”。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=33074\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">注：手机默认设置是始终，也就是一直可以正常连接。如果调整休眠策略就会使得在待机时自动断开。</span><span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个选项的含义如下：</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">始终：一直保持</span><span>WLAN</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的连接。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">仅限充电时：只有在充电时才一直保持连接，如果不充电，待机后</span><span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟断开连接。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">从不（会增加数据网络流量）：待机后</span><span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟断开连接。</span> \n</p>\n<br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":3,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2489","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1398666991000,"seriesProductName":"G610-U00","visitedTimes":721,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"G610-U00(G610+)","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}